## Environment Variables (for web-admin)

Create `.env` file in web-admin:
```env
VITE_API_URL=https://your-project.vercel.app
```

Or set in Netlify:
- Go to Site settings → Environment variables
- Add: `VITE_API_URL` = `https://your-project.vercel.app`

